question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Berapa banyak orang yang tinggal di Odense Municipality, Denmark pada tanggal 1 Juli 2022?
answer: Pada tanggal 1 Juli 2022, Odense Municipality di Denmark memiliki populasi sekitar 205.797 orang.
answer_translated_eng: As of 1 July 2022, Odense Municipality in Denmark had a population of approximately 205,797 people.
